quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,62,"He…ďe ngoo…óndirana on Alla fii yo …ďe mbeltin on. Ko Alla -e Nulaa…óo makko on- …ďuri haan dude e weltineede, si …ďe laatike gooŇč…óin…ďe."
  9,63,"E …ďe nganndaa won de mo lunnduki Alla e Nulaa…óo makko on, haray no woodani mo Yiite Jahannama, ko o luttoowo e magge? Ko …óum woni koyeera maw…óo."
  9,64,"Naafigee…ďe …ďeen no kuli nde cortewol(simoore) Jippintee e ma…ď…ďe ngol no humpita …ďe ko woni e …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe. Maaku : "njalkitee, pellet, Alla ko yaltinoowo kon ko kulu…óon (wata jippo)".(suhritde on)"
  9,65,"Si a la…ďndike …ďe, …ďe mbi'ay: "nganndee men laatinoke mi…óen jumpa mi…óen fija." maaku : "E ko Alla, e Aayeeje makko …óeen e nulaa…óo makko on laatino…óon ho…óon njalkita?"
  9,66,"Wota on ngantino: goo…óii on njddii …ďaawo goo…óinal mon. Si minn njaafike fedde goo e moo…óon, minn leptat fedde wo…ónde tawde kam…ďe …ďe laatinoke bonnoo…ďe."
  9,67,"Naafigi'en wor…ďe, e naafigi'en rew…ďe, yoga ma…ď…ďe no jeyaa e yaga. He…ďe njamira Ňči√Īere, …ďe ka…óa mo∆ī∆īere, he…ďe tama juu…óe ma…ď…ďe. …ďe yejjitii Alla, KaŇčko kadi o yejjiti …ďe. Pellet, naafigii…ďe …ďen ko kam…ďe ngoni yaltu…ďe. …óoftaare."
  9,68,"Alla fodanii naafigee…ďe'en wor…ďe, e naafigee…ďe rew…ďe, e heefer…ďe …ďeen, Yiite Jahannama, ko …ďe luttintee…ďe toon.Nge yonii …ďe. Alla hu…óii …ďe, hino woodani …ďe lepte duumii…óe."